Technigen Platinum corp said itinitial results of a 13-hole drilling program on its R.M. Nicelplatinum property in Rouyn-Noranda, Quebec, indicate"extensive" near-surface zones "highly" enriched in gold,platinum and palladium were found in rocks on the periphery ofa sulphide deposit.    It said values of up to 0.073 ounce of platinum, 0.206ounce palladium, three pct copper and 4.5 pct nickel were foundover a drill section of 13 feet.                   More&#3;